| PAMP.BA | 18% | +2.2% | +3.1% |
| SUPV.BA | 12% | +1.4% | +2.2% |
| BMA | 15% | +1.8% | +2.8% |
| CEPU.BA | 23% | +3.0% | +4.1% |
| **Total** | **100%** | **+12.5%** | **18.0%** |

